snippet: Meeting the deadline was another in a series of steps that Iran promised to take as part of the nuclear agreement reached in July with six world powers.
abstract: International Atomic Energy Agency announces Iran has complied with deadline for submitting information on history of its nuclear program, as required by recent agreement.
lead_paragraph: Meeting the deadline was another in a series of steps that Iran promised to take as part of the nuclear agreement reached in July with six world powers.

headline.main: Iran Meets Atomic Agency Deadline for Material on Past Activities
